T02TD3754E:89a-1: ma h'a yaksha aa pa ra dze rta s'a bha nam tantra /
T02TD3754E:89a-3: gnod sbyin chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i sgrub thabs kyi rgyud /
T02TD3754E:89a-4: dpal phyag na do rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3754E:89a-5: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis nor bdag gi sgrub thabs 'di gsungs so //
T02TD3754E:89a-6: nor rgyas par 'dod pa gang dag gis gnas dben zhing nyams dga' ba'i sar mandal legs par byas te /
T02TD3754E:89a-12: sil snyan bkod pa'i dbus su bum pa mdzes pa 'o ma dang /
T02TD3754E:89b-0: chus bkang ste ldum lcug dang bcas pa snam bu gtsang mas @89b dkris te /
T02TD3754E:89b-1: srad bu sngon po btags la phyag na rdo rje bsnyen par bya ste /
T02TD3754E:89b-2: yid bzhin nor bu 'bum du bzlas la bdag nyid la dbang bskur bar bya'o //
T02TD3754E:89b-3: aom tsanda ma h'a ro sha na h'um phat /
T02TD3754E:89b-4: de nas nor lha nyid bsgrub pa ni khang bu shin tu dben par dkyil 'khor gru bzhi la ba'i rnam lngas byugs te /
T02TD3754E:89b-5: de la padma 'dab brgyad lte ba dang bcas pa bri /
T02TD3754E:89b-6: lte ba dkar po 'dab ma brgyad ser por bya'o //
T02TD3754E:89b-7: de la rin po che'i me tog dgram /
T02TD3754E:89b-8: dbus su bum pa dgod / steng du sku gzhag / mdun du zan dkar po'i gtor ma dkar gsum dang /
T02TD3754E:89b-9: mngar gsum tshod ma sna tshogs dang dri dang rtsi sman gyis brgyan te gzhag go ;
T02TD3754E:89b-10: / mchod pa'i rdzas dag kyang dgod la /
T02TD3754E:89b-11: dang po byang chub tu sems bskyed de /
T02TD3754E:89b-12: dpal phyag na rdo rje bskyed rim ji lta ba bzhin bsgoms pa'i mdun du pam las rin po che'i padma'i lte ba la hr'i: dkar dmar las skyes pa'i nor lha zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3754E:89b-13: dkar zhing dmar ba'i mdangs dang ldan pa phyag g-yas pas rdo rje lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
T02TD3754E:89b-14: g-yon gyis rin chen bee d'urya'o //
T02TD3754E:89b-15: rin po che'i gdan la 'bab bzhugs kyis skyil krung du bzhugs pa /
T02TD3754E:89b-16: gsus po che byis pa'i gzugs lta bu can /
T02TD3754E:89b-17: bzhin mdzes pa spyan 'bur la che ba /
T02TD3754E:89b-18: rin po che'i rgyan gyis kun du bklubs pa'i dam tshig gi gnod sbyin chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa bsams la /
T02TD3754E:89b-19: bdag dang g-yog po'i dpral bar aom /
T02TD3754E:89b-23: gsang bar phat kyis bsrungs te ye shes dgug gzhug bya'o //
T02TD3754E:89b-24: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po kun gyi rgyal //
T02TD3754E:89b-25: gnod sbyin chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa ;
T02TD3754E:89b-26: / gnas 'dir mchod pa 'bul gyis myur du sbyon //
T02TD3754E:89b-27: bdag la zas nor stsol zhing bzhugs su sbyon //
T02TD3754E:89b-28: ae hye hi yaksha aa pa r'a dzi ta sa pa ri w'a ra a'a gatstsha ya a'a gatstsha ya h'um dza /
T02TD3754E:89b-29: des ni mdun du byon par bltas te /
T02TD3754E:89b-30: bdud bsal ba'i phyir rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya'am yungs kar 'phang zhing aom a'a:pi ghn'an ta krit h'um phat ces pas rnam par phye nas mchod yon phul te /
T02TD3754E:89b-31: dam tshig la mngon par bcug la mchod pa phul nas bstod pa byas te /
T02TD3754E:89b-32: aom gnod sbyin chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
T02TD3754E:89b-33: zhal gcig phyag gnyis byis pa'i gzugs 'dra can //
T02TD3754E:90a-0: phyag g-yon yid bzhin rin chen @90a * //
T02TD3754E:90a-2: thugs kar 'dzin mdzad mi zad nor gyi bdag / phyag g-yas lcags kyu 'dzin zhing rgyal pa dang //
T02TD3754E:90a-3: btsun mo la sogs dgug dang dbang du mdzad //
T02TD3754E:90a-4: dung mdog 'od 'phro rin chen rgyan mdzes ldan //
T02TD3754E:90a-5: rin chen gdan la rgyal sras skyil krung bzhugs //
T02TD3754E:90a-6: 'jig rten zas nor kun gyi bdag po ste //
T02TD3754E:90a-7: gang gis khyod bsgrub phongs pa'i 'jigs sel mdzod //
T02TD3754E:90a-8: nor lha'i rgyal po bkra shis 'byung ba'i gnas //
T02TD3754E:90a-9: 'jam pa'i rdo rje khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3754E:90a-10: de'i rjes la rgyal ba sras bcas mchod la /
T02TD3754E:90a-11: de dag gis lha mo mngon par sbrul te bum pa lha'i bdud rtsis bkang bas mngon par bkrus par bsam mo //
T02TD3754E:90a-12: spyi bor dpal phyag na rdo rjes rgyas gdab bo //
T02TD3754E:90a-14: skad che bar ma yin chung bar ma yin myur bar ma yin bul bar ma yin par smra ba bcad cing rnam par g-yeng pa la sogs pa spangs te bzlas so //
T02TD3754E:90a-15: aom hrim phrim aa pa ra dzi ta dza dza h'um phat /
T02TD3754E:90a-16: bzlas pa gtong ba'i dus su mchod pa phul la gtor ma yang sbyin te /
T02TD3754E:90a-17: gtor snod bhr'um las rin po cher bsam /
T02TD3754E:90a-20: h'um gis bdud rtsir bsgyur te phyag na rdo rje la rang sngags kyis dbul /
T02TD3754E:90a-21: gnod sbyin nor lha la sngags aom hri dza yaksha aa pa ra dzi ta sa pa ri w'a ra aa mri ta ba lim kha kha kh'a hi kh'a hi dam ba lim bhaksha yam /
T02TD3754E:90a-22: ma ma ba su pushtim ku ru sarba dza ga ba shingku ru ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD3754E:90a-23: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dharm'a n'am a'adya nutpan na tv'at aom a'a:h'um phat sv'a h'a zhes pa dang /
T02TD3754E:90a-24: tshigs su bcad pas kyang bsngos la /
T02TD3754E:90a-25: bstod pa bya chos bshad de phrin las bcol /
T02TD3754E:90a-26: aom bh'u ta hri ya pa ra dzi ta ratna na ma sarba tri sampa ti sv'a h'a zhes pa brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas te bskul lo //
T02TD3754E:90a-27: de nas dge ba bsngos la aa pa ra dzi ta badzra mu:/
T02TD3754E:90a-28: zhes pas gshegs su gsol lo //
T02TD3754E:90a-29: thun gnyis pa la sogs pa la dam tshig chig rdzogs su bskyed la /
T02TD3754E:90a-30: ye shes dgug pa la sogs pa sngar bzhin du bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90a-31: tshes gcig nas bco lnga'i bar du bsgrub bo //
T02TD3754E:90a-32: bco lnga'i zhag gi dang po nas tho rangs kyi bar du sngags rgyun ma chad par bzlas /
T02TD3754E:90a-33: lce pog dkar po'i bdug pa dbul /
T02TD3754E:90b-0: tho rangs grub pa'i rtags snang ba ni rab gzugs mngon sum du ston te bdag gis ji ltar bya zer te sgrub pa pos bdag gi bka' nyon @90b cig bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90b-1: mna' bsgag dam chu blud ci 'dod pa bcol /
T02TD3754E:90b-2: rgyal mtshan gyi phyag rgya bstan te phan chad bka' nyan te de la zhon nas tshangs pa'i 'jig rten mthong ngo //
T02TD3754E:90b-3: lha'i gnas su bskyal nas lha'i dbang pos dbang skur bar byed do //
T02TD3754E:90b-5: gzugs sgra gang byung yang skrag par mi bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90b-6: de lta bu'i mtshan ma ma byung na nam langs pa'i dus su rmi lam brtag / des ma grub na phyi ma'i zla ba la de bzhin du bsgrub /
T02TD3754E:90b-7: des kyang ma grub na yang phyi ma'i zla ba la bsgrub bo //
T02TD3754E:90b-8: de nas dngos grub ni rab rig pa'i rgyal po'i dbang thob bo //
T02TD3754E:90b-13: dgra dang nad thams cad zhi bar byed do //
T02TD3754E:90b-14: tshe ring ba bskal pa bdun thub par 'gyur /
T02TD3754E:90b-15: nor mang ba zad pa med cing dpag tu med pa brjod kyis mi lang bar 'byor ro //
T02TD3754E:90b-16: gal te gnod par byed pa byung na yang khros pa tsam gyis de ma thag tu 'chi bar byed do //
T02TD3754E:90b-17: 'bring ni lta sgom gyi nyams myong skye /
T02TD3754E:90b-18: bud med thams cad dbang du 'gyur zhing nor gyis phyug par 'gyur /
T02TD3754E:90b-19: bkra shis par byed pa dang dgra 'chi bar yang byed do //
T02TD3754E:90b-20: tha ma yang nor 'phel par byed cing dgra 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD3754E:90b-21: grub nas rtag tu bsten pa ni zla ba nya gang ba thams cad la gtor ma gtang bar bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90b-22: dngos grub gang byung ba de cha drug tu bgos te bla ma dang dkon mchog gsum spyi dang /
T02TD3754E:90b-23: sems can dag la cha re re sbyin /
T02TD3754E:90b-24: phyed kyis sgrub pa po'i 'tsho ba bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90b-25: sgrub pa'i dus su zas dkar gsum bza' zhing gtsang sbra dang ldan par bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90b-26: rtag tu khrus la brtson par bya'o ;
T02TD3754E:90b-27: /'di grub na yon tan dpag tu med do //
T02TD3754E:90b-28: 'di la gdeng bzhi dang ldan pas 'grub ste /
T02TD3754E:90b-29: mgo gnon ye shes bsnyen pa'i gdeng /
T02TD3754E:90b-31: mi nyams pa dam tshig gi gdeng /
T02TD3754E:90b-32: the tshom med pa nges pa'i gdeng ngo //
T02TD3754E:90b-33: de la lta ba ni chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bur shes par bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90b-34: dam tshig ni bla ma mnyes par bya zhing gsang la sgrub ste /
T02TD3754E:90b-35: gzhan la thabs 'di bstan par mi bya'o //
T02TD3754E:90b-36: gnod sbyin chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i sgrub thabs kyi rgyud rdzogs so /
T02TD3754E:90b-38: // / rgya gar gyi bla ma dz'a m'a ris bsgyur ba'o//
